skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: titanium rex
des:
Titanium Rex (voiced by Bryan Cranston) is an aging super hero who has long been the head of the League of Freedom, a once-proud assembly of super heroes that isn’t what it used to be. 

In this skill, you can ask Titanium Rex for the answers to life’s most pressing questions! Ask any “yes” or “no” question, learn about the show, or hear sage advice from the world’s greatest <cough> super hero.

SuperMansion is a stop-motion animated series created by Stoopid Buddy Stoodios, the team behind Robot Chicken, and available for streaming only on Crackle.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
